OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FThis month is on track to see the
OL,7,Fhighest number of homes being freshly
OL,8,Flisted for sale in February for a
OL,9,Fdecade, according to a property
OL,10,Fwebsite.
OL,12,FZoopla has recorded 6% more homes for
OL,13,Fsale in the four weeks to February 15
OL,14,Fcompared with the same period in 2025.
OL,16,FCombined with falling mortgage rates,
OL,17,Fthe market is currently looking
OL,18,Fparticularly good for first-time
OL,19,Fbuyers, the website said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
