OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771995859
OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FIt said the surge in homes for sale
OL,7,Fwill increase choice for buyers and
OL,8,Fhelp keep price increases in check
OL,9,Fthis year.
OL,11,FMany lenders have also made changes to
OL,12,Ftheir criteria, allowing some people
OL,13,Fto borrow more.
OL,15,FThe number of sales being agreed has
OL,16,Fincreased sharply, but remains below
OL,17,Fthe "very strong start" to 2025, the
OL,18,Freport said.
OL,26,@yD@EOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
