OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771995859
OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FSales are currently running at the
OL,7,Ffourth strongest February level in the
OL,8,Fpast decade, even though there are
OL,9,Ffewer buyers in the market than a year
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,FZoopla estimated 40% of homes
OL,13,Fcurrently for sale on its website are
OL,14,Fcheaper to buy with a mortgage than
OL,15,Fthe cost of renting locally, assuming
OL,16,Fsomeone has a 20% deposit to put down,
OL,17,Fwhich is an improvement compared with
OL,18,F25% last year. People's individual
OL,19,Fcircumstances will vary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
