OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FHouse prices increased by 1.3% in the
OL,7,F12 months to January, Zoopla said,
OL,8,Franging from an 8.0% rise in Northern
OL,9,FIreland to a 0.2% fall in London.
OL,11,FWithin Britain, the North West of
OL,12,FEngland was identified as the
OL,13,Fstrongest-performing region, with
OL,14,Fprices up 3.3% annually, followed by
OL,15,FScotland (2.8%) and the North East
OL,16,F(2.5%).
OL,18,FIn Wales, house prices increased by
OL,19,F2.2% annually.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771995859
OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FThe areas with higher price growth are
OL,7,Fmore affordable and have fewer homes
OL,8,Ffor sale than a year ago, limiting
OL,9,Fbuyer choice and supporting price
OL,10,Fgrowth, Zoopla said.
OL,12,FLooking at southern England, where
OL,13,Faffordability is more stretched, the
OL,14,Freport said: "Sellers in southern
OL,15,FEngland who are planning to move this
OL,16,Fyear will need to price realistically
OL,17,Fto secure a timely sale and should
OL,18,Ffactor this into the offer they make
OL,19,Fon their next purchase."
OL,26,@vD@NOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
