OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FZoopla's house price index uses sold
OL,7,Fprices, mortgage valuations and data
OL,8,Ffor agreed sales to make calculations.
OL,10,FRichard Donnell, executive director at
OL,11,FZoopla, said: "Despite improved levels
OL,12,Fof market activity, subdued house
OL,13,Fprice inflation is good news for
OL,14,Fbuyers and sellers and represents a
OL,15,Fmore stable market. More sellers
OL,16,Fputting their home on the market shows
OL,17,Fa strong desire to move home.
OL,26,@sD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1771995859
OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,F"Lower mortgage rates and improved
OL,7,Faffordability of mortgages means now
OL,8,Fcould very well be the best time to
OL,9,Fbuy a home in recent years, especially
OL,10,Ffor first-time buyers with more homes
OL,11,Favailable to buy for less than the
OL,12,Fcost of renting.
OL,14,F"We expect continued modest rates of
OL,15,Fprice inflation over 2026, which will
OL,16,Fsupport healthy levels of sales with
OL,17,Fsome wide variations across local
OL,18,Fmarkets. Sellers need to seek the
OL,19,Fadvice of local agents to get the
OL,20,Fright strategy for their home."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
