OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FDavid Fell, lead analyst at property
OL,7,Ffirm Hamptons said: "With the
OL,8,Fadvantage of not having a home to
OL,9,Fsell, first-time buyers have often
OL,10,Fbeen favoured by sellers above others
OL,11,Fmaking offers at a similar level.
OL,13,F"This has allowed first-time buyers to
OL,14,Fnegotiate harder than they have
OL,15,Fpreviously. In February, a fifth were
OL,16,Fable to secure a discount of 10% or
OL,17,Fmore from the asking price."
OL,26,@oD@UOUuD@AOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
