OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FNigel Bishop, founder of buying agency
OL,7,FRecoco Property Search, said: "Whilst
OL,8,Fprices have seen a subtle increase,
OL,9,Fthe uplift in homes for sale will
OL,10,Fallow more buyers to hold the upper
OL,11,Fhand during price negotiations."
OL,13,FTom Bill, head of UK residential
OL,14,Fresearch at Knight Frank, said: "House
OL,15,Fprices are being kept in check by
OL,16,Frising supply as plans delayed by last
OL,17,Fyear's budget are activated and more
OL,18,Flandlords attempt to sell due to red
OL,19,Ftape.
OL,26,@oD@_OUsD@`O]vD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
