OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,F"Buyers are more circumspect than
OL,7,Fsellers but further mortgage rate
OL,8,Fdeclines and increasingly realistic
OL,9,Fasking prices will support
OL,10,Ftransactions this spring."
OL,12,FAlastair Douglas, TotallyMoney chief
OL,13,Fexecutive said: "Falling mortage rates
OL,14,Fand more homes on the market is good
OL,15,Fnews for those who can get on the
OL,16,Fhousing ladder. But for millions of
OL,17,Fyoung people, the problem isn't the
OL,18,Frate ` it's getting a mortgage in the
OL,19,Ffirst place."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@ZO]uD@QOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
