OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FNathan Emerson, chief executive of
OL,7,Fproperty professionals body
OL,8,FPropertymark, said: "With inflation
OL,9,Fdipping down earlier this month, it is
OL,10,Fhoped the Bank of England may have the
OL,11,Fconfidence to bring the base rate down
OL,12,Ffurther when they next meet."
