OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,FJen Lloyd, head of mortgage products
OL,7,Fand propositions at Skipton Building
OL,8,FSociety, said: "More homes coming onto
OL,9,Fthe market gives people taking their
OL,10,Ffirst step on the ladder greater
OL,11,Fchoice, and helps create a healthier,
OL,12,Fmore accessible housing market for
OL,13,Fpeople taking their first step onto
OL,14,Fthe ladder.
OL,26,@pD@POU
