OL,3,CZoopla seeing strongest February in
OL,4,Cdecade for new property listings
OL,6,F"At Skipton, we're already seeing this
OL,7,Frenewed confidence reflected in our
OL,8,Fown data. Applications from firsttime
OL,9,Fbuyers in January 2026 were up 42%
OL,10,Fcompared with the same period last
OL,11,Fyear, showing that more people are
OL,12,Ffeeling ready, and able, to make their
OL,13,Fmove.
OL,15,F"With increased supply and improving
OL,16,Fmarket conditions, 2026 is shaping up
OL,17,Fto be a far more encouraging year for
OL,18,Fthose trying to buy their first home."
OL,20,FHere are annual price changes,
OL,21,Faccording to Zoopla:
